title: Cytokinetics: 1Q Earnings Snapshot
text:
SOUTH SAN FRANCISCO, Calif. (AP) _ Cytokinetics Inc. (CYTK) on Thursday reported a loss of $30.3 million in its first quarter.
The South San Francisco, California-based company said it had a loss of 56 cents per share.
The biopharmaceutical company posted revenue of $5.3 million in the period.
Cytokinetics shares have declined 5.5 percent since the beginning of the year. The stock has fallen 54 percent in the last 12 months.
